1. *Vidite* li da je sunce već izašlo? (Do you see that the sun has already come out?)

2. Oni će *videti* koliko su dobili na ispitu. (They will see how much they got on the test.)

3. Ona je *videla* da je njena sestra tužna. (She saw that her sister was sad.)

4. *Videće* li oni da su zašli u pogrešnu ulicu? (Will they see that they have entered the wrong street?)

5. Ono što ćeš *videti* će te uzbuđivati. (What you will see will excite you.)